Package: OxfordApi
Type: Package
Title: Methods for Using the Oxford Dictionaries API
Version: 0.0.1
Authors@R: c(
    person("Benjamin", "Nutter", email = "benjamin.nutter@gmail.com", 
           role = c("aut", "ctb", "cre")))
Maintainer: Benjamin Nutter <benjamin.nutter@gmail.com>
Description: The Oxford Dictionaries API provides access words, definitions,
  and usage of the English language.  Functions in this package provide 
  a simplified and consistent interface to make use of the API.
